PN,39201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,FScientists in Manchester have
OL,8,Fdiscovered one of the most common
OL,9,Fgenetic causes of severe epilepsy,
OL,10,Festimating it could allow thousands to
OL,11,Fbe diagnosed globally.
OL,13,FAva Begley, 6, is one of over 80
OL,14,Fpeople who have been diagnosed with
OL,15,Fthe condition in the "landmark
OL,16,Fbreakthrough".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,FHer parents - Daniel Begley and
OL,8,FElizabeth Dowd, from Sydney, Australia
OL,9,F- said they feel "deeply grateful"
OL,10,Fthat the researchers, from Manchester
OL,11,FUniversity NHS Foundation Trust (MFT)
OL,12,Fand The University of Manchester
OL,13,F(UoM), have made this discovery, which
OL,14,Fis one of the most common genetic
OL,15,Fcauses of severe epilepsy.
OL,17,FThey said: "Our first reaction was a
OL,18,Fmixture of emotion ` relief at finally
OL,19,Fhaving a diagnosis, but also sadness
OL,20,Fin understanding the seriousness of
OL,21,Fthe condition and how rare it is.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,F"Above all, we felt grateful that
OL,8,FAva's experience may contribute to
OL,9,Fgreater knowledge and future progress
OL,10,Fand treatment."
OL,12,FAva has lived with developmental
OL,13,Fdelay, intellectual disability and
OL,14,Fsevere epilepsy with frequent seizures
OL,15,Fsince she early childhood, and
OL,16,Frequires full-time care. She had up to
OL,17,F200 seizures a day which are now
OL,18,Fcontrolled with medication.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,FShe is non-verbal and cannot
OL,8,Fcommunicate through speech or
OL,9,Fgestures; experiences major motor and
OL,10,Fbalance difficulties and can only walk
OL,11,Fshort distances.
OL,13,FResearchers in Manchester collaborated
OL,14,Fwith the Sydney Children's Hospital
OL,15,FClinical Genetics Team to link Ava's
OL,16,Fcondition to the newly identified
OL,17,Frecessive RNU2-2-related disorder.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,FHer parents said she "is a beautiful
OL,8,Flittle girl with a bright presence.
OL,9,FShe loves looking through books,
OL,10,Fmusic, sensory play, being outdoors,
OL,11,Fand spending time with her family.
OL,12,FEven with the immense challenges she
OL,13,Ffaces, Ava brings extraordinary love
OL,14,Fand meaning into our lives. She has a
OL,15,Fdeep presence about her that touches
OL,16,Feveryone who meets her.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,F"For many years we have been through
OL,8,Fextensive medical investigations,
OL,9,Fspecialist appointments, and genetic
OL,10,Ftesting, hoping to find an answer that
OL,11,Fcould explain Ava's condition and
OL,12,Fguide her care. Like many rare disease
OL,13,Ffamilies, we have lived with a long
OL,14,Fperiod of uncertainty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,F"Having a diagnosis is incredibly
OL,8,Fmeaningful. It gives Ava a name and a
OL,9,Fplace in the medical world, rather
OL,10,Fthan being an unanswered mystery. It
OL,11,Fhelps us feel that we are getting
OL,12,Fcloser to the starting point of being
OL,13,Fable to find a cure/treatment, and
OL,14,Fprovides hope that research and
OL,15,Fawareness may lead to better
OL,16,Funderstanding and support in the
OL,17,Ffuture.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,F"We believe that rare disease research
OL,8,Fis vital, not only for families like
OL,9,Fours, but for the broader medical
OL,10,Fcommunity. Ava's journey has been
OL,11,Fchallenging, but she is deeply loved,
OL,12,Fand we are committed to advocating for
OL,13,Fher and for all children living with
OL,14,Frare and complex conditions."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,FThe new condition, which the
OL,8,Fresearchers have named as "Recessive
OL,9,FRNU2-2-related neurodevelopmental
OL,10,Fdisorder", results in difficult-to-
OL,11,Fcontrol seizures and severe
OL,12,Fdevelopmental delays in children,
OL,13,Foften appearing within their first
OL,14,Fyear of life.
OL,16,FThe research has lead to the diagnosis
OL,17,Fof the condition for 84 people around
OL,18,Fthe world, and experts estimate
OL,19,Fthousands of people remain undiagnosed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,FThey say that millions of people
OL,8,Fglobally could be "carriers" of the
OL,9,Ffaulty gene behind this disorder.
OL,11,FStudy lead and first author of the
OL,12,Fpaper Dr Adam Jackson said: "We
OL,13,Fbelieve that as many as in 1 in 100
OL,14,Fpeople could unknowingly be carriers
OL,15,Fof this condition. If both parents are
OL,16,Fcarriers, there is a 1 in 4 chance
OL,17,Fwith every pregnancy that their child
OL,18,Fcould be affected.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,F"We estimate roughly 1 in 40,000
OL,8,Fpeople may be living with this
OL,9,Fcondition, making it one of the most
OL,10,Fcommon neurodevelopmental disorders
OL,11,Fcurrently known. Our discovery brings
OL,12,Fhope for many patients and families
OL,13,Fwho have been searching for answers
OL,14,Fand is already having a positive
OL,15,Fimpact around the world."
OL,26,@wD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,F"What makes this discovery even more
OL,8,Fremarkable is that RNU2-2 is extremely
OL,9,Fsmall in comparison to other genes.
OL,10,FUnlike most other genes, RNU2-2 does
OL,11,Fnot even make a protein. We were
OL,12,Fastonished to discover how changes in
OL,13,Fthis tiny gene can have such profound
OL,14,Feffects in so many individuals."
OL,16,FChildren with the condition experience
OL,17,Fsevere epilepsy early on in life,
OL,18,Foften in their first year. It can
OL,19,Fcause seizures which can be difficult
OL,20,Fto fully control with medication.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,FThe condition also has a profound
OL,8,Fimpact on brain development, causing
OL,9,Fdelays or inability to achieve key
OL,10,Fmilestones such as walking or talking.
OL,11,FAlmost all affected individuals have
OL,12,Fsignificant learning problems.
OL,14,FStudy lead and senior author Professor
OL,15,FSiddharth Banka said: "Our work helps
OL,16,Fexpand knowledge of conditions related
OL,17,Fto RNU genes, an emerging group of
OL,18,Fdiseases which potentially affect
OL,19,Faround 1 in 10,000 individuals
OL,20,Fglobally.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1774872666
OL,3,CGirl, 6, receives diagnosis for
OL,4,Cgenetic epilepsy in 'landmark
OL,5,Cbreakthrough'
OL,7,F"It also shines a light on the regions
OL,8,Fof the human genome sometimes
OL,9,Fdismissed as 'junk DNA'. We now see
OL,10,Fthat so-called 'dark regions' are
OL,11,Fvital for health."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
